ions. Audit records shall preserve enough traceability for reviewers to understand what capability was invoked, what boundary or policy applied, and why a request was allowed, stopped, or denied.\nExplicitly deny raw export, raw tool access, and unauthorized posting: The product shall explicitly refuse requests for raw Slack API access, raw MCP access, bulk export, and posting to channels outside authorized policy. Denial behavior shall be intentional and user-visible, not an accidental backend failure or silent omission."
